            <div class="title">
                Colonial Naval Defence Bill Lords
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1949-02-22/debates/e76f0c17-3d59-449e-a207-07c69129b400/SocialServices(NorthernIrelandAgreement)Bill" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
