            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-d624b70f-f266-4d7b-83e8-a7509251b246">
                Mr. Emrys Hughes
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-d624b70f-f266-4d7b-83e8-a7509251b246" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
